{
  "text": "35 S]methionine in methionine-deficient RPMI medium, and immunoprecipitated with 9GL-monospecific antibodies as previously described [CITATION_1] . Western blot (immunoblot) analyses of highly purified ASFV virions with 9GL antiserum and antisera against ASFV structural proteins p30 [CITATION_2] and p54 (50) were performed as previously described [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
